                  , then on shore, in the execution of his duty, in seizing for the use of our Lord the King, some foreign spirituous liquors, liable to be seized by the said officers, unlawfully and violently did make an assault on the said 
                     
                        <persName id="t17910608-41-victim454" type="victimName">
