            </rs>.</p>
               <p>STEPHEN, otherwise STREPHON EDWARDS, <rs id="t17910608-41-verdict248" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910608-41-verdict248" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17910608-41-punish249" type="punishmentDescription">
