                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910608-41-defend450 t17910608-41-punish249"></join>
               Imprisoned three years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. Baron PERRYN.</p>
